          <m>\left\{\begin{array}{ccc} \frac13\tanh^{-1}\left(\frac x3\right)+C \amp \amp x^2\lt 9 \\ \\
          \frac13\coth^{-1}\left(\frac x3\right)+C \amp \amp 9\lt x^2
          \end{array} \right. = \frac12\ln |x+1| - \frac12\ln |x-1|+C</m>
